{
  "text": "The estimation process is completely automated: the Web page loading and the component and resource information gathering is done programmatically. Similar to prior modeling work [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , RECON builds predictive models for the user-specic network types (WiFi vs Cellular) and devices.",
